commits.content:
name: flutter_html
description: A Flutter widget rendering static HTML and CSS as Flutter widgets.
version: 3.0.0-alpha.6
homepage: https://github.com/Sub6Resources/flutter_html

environment:
  sdk: '>=3 <3.0.0'
  flutter: '>=2.2.0'

dependencies:
  # Plugin for parsing html
  html: '>=0.15.0 <1.0.0'

  # Plugin for parsing css
  csslib: '>=0.17.0 <1.0.0'

  # Plugin for firstWhereOrNull extension on lists
  collection: '>=1.15.0 <2.0.0'

  # plugin to convert integers to numerals
  numerus: '>=2.0.0 <3.0.0'

  flutter:
    sdk: flutter

dev_dependencies:
  flutter_test:
    sdk: flutter
  flutter_lints: ^2.0.1
  meta: ^1.8.0

flutter:
